rg_etc1
------------------------------------------
rg_etc1.cpp is a ZLIB licensed, performant, easy to use, and high quality 4x4
pixel block packer/unpacker for the ETC1 (Ericsson Texture Compression) texture
compression format written in a single C++ source file. It has no external
compile-time or run-time dependencies on any other library or API, allowing it
to be trivially dropped in to other projects.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  librg_etc1-devel-1.04-1bl2
  librg_etc1_1-1.04-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-3.31.3-1
  cygport-0.37.3-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://code.google.com/archive/p/rg-etc1/

Canonical download:
  https://storage.googleapis.com/google-code-archive-downloads/v2/code.google.com/rg-etc1/rg_etc1_v104.zip

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack rg_etc1-1.04-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./rg_etc1-1.04-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/rg_etc1-1.04-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/rg_etc1-1.04-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librg_etc1_1-1.04-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librg_etc1-devel-1.04-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(rg_etc1)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/rg_etc1.README

(librg_etc1_1)
  /usr/bin/cygrg_etc1-1.dll

(librg_etc1-devel)
  /usr/include/rg_etc1.h
  /usr/lib/librg_etc1.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/rg_etc1.pc

------------------

